Hey all. I'm doing a survey on crypto and non-crypto users. Please fill out this quick survey if you use or DO NoT use crypto. Thank you:) 
<https://forms.gle/1DFfYp35U3jkoVif7|https://forms.gle/1DFfYp35U3jkoVif7>

attachments.title: Crypto Users
attachments.text: Hello! I'm conducting some research to understand how millennials and Gen Z's use cryptocurrency and the role cryptocurrency plays in their life. Please answer honestly to help improve the results of our research. Your individual response will be kept confidential and will not be published, stored, or used for any other purpose outside of this survey and related follow-up research. Based on your response, I may reach out to you for a 20- to 45-minute remote interview on Zoom. You may provide a phone number if you wish to be contacted to participate in this follow-up interview. This survey should take less than 5 minutes. Please email me if you have any questions or concerns at <mailto:hillaryomitogun@gmail.com|hillaryomitogun@gmail.com>. Thanks a lot for helping out :)
